  "title": "Sales Engineer (Water Jetting | Industrial Cleaning)",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li><li><strong>Basic $3500 - $4000 + $1020 Transport + Incentive + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: West</strong></li><li><strong>Working day: Monday to Friday</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: 8.15am to 5.30pm </strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>To market a full range of Professional & Industrial Cleaning equipment, and accessories & tools, to corporate customers, with an emphasis in oil and gas sectors</strong></li><li><strong>Serve existing assigned accounts and prospect potential new customers </strong></li><li>Learn & familiarise our products well, understand users’ needs, and so be able to offer solutions and assistance to meet their requirements</li><li>Perform hands-on product demonstrations, as well as occasionally conduct presentations to mid-size audiences including management levels</li><li>Any ad hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess minimum Polytechnic Diploma or equivalent with minimum 2 years of sales experience, with prior exposure to clients in the petrochemical, oil refinery, shipyard, oil & gas industries</li><li><strong>Possess Class 3 driving license and own vehicle </strong></li></ul><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)<br />EA Recruitment Pte Ltd<br />EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
